Liverpool take on Everton in the first Merseyside Derby of the season on Wednesday night. The Reds will be looking to take all three points from their struggling rivals, especially after Manchester City thrashed Burnley 4-1 on Tuesday. For Marco Silva, his job is on the line and he will be desperate to get a result at Anfield. Kick off is 9.15pm West African time. Wednesday, December 4
